sp. n.

6b
Antennal postpedicel orange basally with terminal parts dark red -brown; major macrosetae of male mystax black (some golden -yellow ones may be present) with minor golden -yellow setae laterally; female mystax extensively golden yellow. Illustrations - Hypopygium (
Figs 13-15
), T2 (
Fig. 38
), Distribution (
Fig. 49
) ..... 

